Vice President Kamala Harris received a booster shot and encourages others to do the same when eligible. She emphasizes that the vaccines are free, safe, and life-saving. Harris mentions the heartbreaking videos of unvaccinated people in ICU beds begging others, including their own family members, to get vaccinated. She highlights that over 90 percent of those in ICUs or dying from COVID-19 are unvaccinated. Harris urges everyone to get vaccinated to overcome the pandemic.